  В«TD5В» В«APL 1 + 3В»
        В«APL вҠЈ 1 + 3В»

 В«TRВ»
  В«TD1В»В«BO PartitionВ» В«В»
        Z is B, divided into partitions according to A. Two elements B[b]
        and B[b+1] of B belong to the same partition if A[b] вүҘ A[b+1] > 0.
        Each partition becomes a nested item of Z where B[b] with A[b] = 0
        are removed.
  В«TD2В»В«APL 1 1  2 2  3 3 3 3 вҠӮ 'ABCDEFGH'   вҚқ 3 partitionsВ»
       В«APL 1 1  0 0  3 3 3 3 вҠӮ 'ABCDEFGH'   вҚқ 2 partitionsВ»
  В«TD3В» вҠӮ
  В«TD4В»В«BO EncloseВ»В«В»Z is B for simple scalars B, otherwise a scalar
                     that contains B as a nested value
  В«TD5В»В«APL BвҶҗ3 4 вҚҙ5В»
       В«APL 8 вҺ•CR BВ»
       В«APL 8 вҺ•CR вҠӮBВ»

 В«TRВ»
  В«TD1В»В«BO PickВ» В«В»
        Z is a nested sub-value of B, whose position in B is determined by A.
        Every item of A corresponds to a nesting level of B.
  В«TD2В»В«APL 8 вҺ•CR  SвҶҗ2 3ПҒ'AB' 'CD' 'EF' 'GH' 'IJ' 'KL'В»
       В«APL (1 3) 2 вҠғ S   вҚқ (1 3) selects 'EF' from S, 2 selects 'F' from 'EF'В»
       В«APL (вҠғS[1;3])[2]   вҚқ the same.В»

  В«TD3В» вҠғ
  В«TD4В»В«BO DiscloseВ»В«В»
        Z is the elements of B,
        with nested sub-values
        replaced by arrays padded
        to the same common size
  В«TD5В» В«APL 8 вҺ•CR BвҶҗ2 2вҚҙ'One' 'Two' 'Three' 'Four'В»
        В«APL 8 вҺ•CR вҠғ BВ»

 В«TRВ»
  В«TD1В»В«BO RotateВ»В«В»Z is B rotated according to A
  В«TD2В»В«APL вҠўBвҶҗ3 5вҚҙвҚі5В»
       В«APL 1 2 3вҢҪB       вҚқ rotate along the last axis (columns)В»
       В«APL ВҜ1 ВҜ2 ВҜ3вҢҪB    вҚқ rotate backwards along the last axis (columns)В»
       В«APL вҠўBвҶҗ3/вҚӘвҚі5В»
       В«APL 1 2 3вҠ–B       вҚқ rotate along the first axis (rows)В»
  В«TD3В» вҠ– В«В» вҢҪ
  В«TD4В»В«BO ReverseВ»В«В»
        Z is B with the items along the first resp. last axis reversed
  В«TD5В»В«APL вҢҪ1 2 3 4 5В»

 В«TRВ»
  В«TD1В»В«BO Transpose (General)В»В«В»Z is B transposed according to A.
       В«В» A is a vector of
          numbers inВ«В»
          1 2 3...вҢҲ/A (or inВ«В»
          0 1 2..., if вҺ•IOвҶҗ0).
          В«В»В«В»
          Permutations A (of
          вҚівҚҙвҚҙB) permute the
          axes of B.
          В«В»В«В»
          Repeated items in A
          select diagonals in
