В«H4 List of Built-in Monadic APL OperatorВ»

A monadic APL operator OP1 takes 2 or 3 arguments in the following order:

В«UL
В«LI a left value В«BO AВ» (mandatory or optional, depending on the operator),В»
В«LI a mandatory left function argument В«BO fВ» (followed by the operator itself)В»
В«LI a mandatory right value В«BO BВ».В»
В»

