  В«TD1В»В«BO Reduce N-wiseВ» В«В»
        Like В«BO f/BВ» and В«BO fвҢҝBВ» except that В«BO fВ» is applied to groups
        CВ«su 1В» CВ«su 2В» ... CВ«su nВ».
        Each group CВ«su nВ» has A consecutive items of B and starts at position
        i of the axis along which the N-wise reductions are computed.
