В«H4 List of Built-In Dyadic APL OperatorsВ»

A dyadic APL operator OP2 takes 3 or 4 arguments in the following order:

В«UL
В«LI a left value В«BO AВ» (mandatory or optional, depending on the operator),В»
В«LI a mandatory function argument В«BO fВ», (followed by the operator itself)В»
